  76:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pcd_ex.c ****       When a TxFIFO is not used, the Configuration should be as follows:
  77:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pcd_ex.c ****           case 1 :  n > m    and Txn is not used    (n,m  : Transmit FIFO indexes)
  78:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pcd_ex.c ****          --> Txm can use the space allocated for Txn.
